node.text:
Offered by @Nestseekers📍12 Barrow Place, Southampton NY $7,995,000
__
Situated on 2.07 acres with it's own private beach, this +/- 4220 sqft home is the perfect Hampton's paradise.

With several windows and sliding glass doors, this modern home presents undeniable natural lighting while seamlessly incorporating the breathtaking Shinnecock Bay views into the interior design. The large kitchen offers a large island, and bar seating.

The dining area leads to a spacious great room with a wet bar, all of which cater to the expansive views. The generous master suite with en-suite master bathroom offers sliding glass doors situated in-front of the soaking tub, providing a spa-inspired, relaxing experience.

The large backyard, impeccable landscaping, and poolside patio provide exceptional opportunities for entertaining including tennis.
-

node.text:
Offered by @Nestseekers 📍367 Mizner Lake Estates Drive, Boca Raton FL $6,750,000
__
This home is designed to inspire. The generously proportioned residence provides an abundance of possibilities from quiet relaxation to gracious entertaining, both indoors and out. The interior boasts a modern take on the Neoclassical grandeur of Mizner Lake Estates.

A 2021 renovation, including a brand new roof, windows, and landscaping complement the newly renovated open concept kitchen, family room, living room and master bathrooms. These generously proportioned rooms include two private master bedrooms, one pool-side with views of the golf course, and one on the second floor with private balcony.

A fabulous home in the most exclusive private community in Boca Raton. Mizner Lake Estates is preeminently positioned on the grounds of the exquisitely redesigned Boca Resort & Club.
__
